**Feature flag rules:**
⛔ **Never edit `flags.py` directly** — flags are env vars injected at deploy time.
Use `deploy.py flag-add / activate / deactivate / release` only.

**Branch rules:** Short-lived branches. No PRs. Push to main is normal.
